question: Which restaurant is available towards Ancient and Honorable Artillery Company Museum, Boston, MA within 30 kilometers from Dewey Farm Conservation Land, Millis, MA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.364939 42.185888)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.056119 42.360113)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.364939 42.185888)',4326)::geography, 30000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.364939 42.185888)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
